00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:14,679
(He went alone to seek You Chen'an.)

2
00:00:15,160 --> 00:00:17,399
(He fought to the death
to obtain his fingerprint.)

3
00:00:17,839 --> 00:00:20,559
(He traded his life to restore
His Highness and Jing Yi's innocence.)

4
00:00:27,120 --> 00:00:29,359
(While we were investigating
Gao Luoqian's crimes,)

5
00:00:29,760 --> 00:00:30,800
(we discovered in fear that)

6
00:00:31,200 --> 00:00:33,280
(Nanzhao had been laying its plans
in the capital for a long time.)

7
00:00:33,679 --> 00:00:35,280
(Who knows how many
Great Tang officials)

8
00:00:35,399 --> 00:00:36,479
(have already been corrupted)

9
00:00:36,759 --> 00:00:37,399
(and exploited.)

10
00:00:39,840 --> 00:00:41,320
(Jiang Daohai, Prefect of the Capital,)

11
00:00:41,920 --> 00:00:43,880
(was also secretly
colluding with Nanzhao.)

12
00:00:44,759 --> 00:00:45,880
(Their reach)

13
00:00:46,240 --> 00:00:48,200
(has already extended deep
into the imperial relatives.)

14
00:00:48,399 --> 00:00:49,520
(The entanglements run deep.)

15
00:00:49,799 --> 00:00:50,840
(There is no easy place to strike.)

16
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:52,960
(To ensure safety,)

17
00:00:53,600 --> 00:00:55,119
(we could only begin our investigation)

18
00:00:55,320 --> 00:00:57,240
(with his household member,
Zhao Wanrong.)

19
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:16,520
♪Embark on a farewell
without saying goodbye♪

20
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:21,280
♪Build a bridge between life and death♪

21
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:25,560
♪Hear a voiceless declaration♪

22
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:30,760
♪Break disguises, cross illusions♪

23
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:33,680
♪A fleeting life and delusions♪

24
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:36,520
♪The surface always conceals♪

25
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:41,560
♪Separate cause and effect♪

26
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:44,440
♪A twisted path, rising and falling♪

27
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:47,080
♪Seek the path amid the hazy unknown♪

28
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:51,920
♪Writing oblivion with a sharp blade♪

29
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:56,800
♪No matter how far, I gaze at the light♪

30
00:01:57,160 --> 00:02:02,360
♪Fearing no wild lands, I press on♪

31
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:07,840
♪To see the tides of the world
once more♪

32
